            "answer_text": "You should check what information the school requires in the letter first. We were required to provide:Dear (class teacher or school head)re: ABSENTEEISM (FULL NAME OF CHILD) GRADE XXJohnny will not be at school (or did not attend school) on day-of-the-week dd/mm/yyyy beause ...................................................................................................... (he had a dental/doctor appointment) (due to toothache/vomiting).(it helps to add an absenteeism/I have seen Johnny so-and-so on dd/mm/yyy)Should any other information be required, my name and number are listed below.SincerelyMrs (your name)Tel: We were also required to write by hand so the kids couldn't forge your note! ",
